{"TopicId":123034,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"THE single most aggravating thing in KSP for me is...","CreatedByName":"wossname","CreatedById":118005,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-14T19:10:18Z","PageNum":7,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"fireblade274","CreatedById":134571,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-10T22:54:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stoney3k\u0022 data-cite=\u0022stoney3k\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E1.0.5 and the medium landing gear *still* doesn\u0027t have any wheel steering?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ethis.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"panzer1b","CreatedById":95108,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-11T02:54:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/B9Lbs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EJavascript is disabled. View full album\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETHIS IS AN OUTRAGE!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI WANT MY ARMOR BACK!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kurld","CreatedById":79950,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-11T18:21:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022 data-cite=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAll decouplers can now be disabled in the editor by right clicking them and turning them off.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHey, cool!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn 1.05 it is indeed now possible to disable staging for part modules.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor decouplers you can right click the part and do it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou can also do it for engines (I\u0027ve wanted to do it for my launch escape parts for a long time now) by adding the line:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E stagingEnabled = False\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eto the ModuleEnginesFX module for the engine in its part.cfg file.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Goomblah","CreatedById":143441,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-11T18:52:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022panzer1b\u0022 data-cite=\u0022panzer1b\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/a/B9Lbs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/a/B9Lbs\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETHIS IS AN OUTRAGE!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI WANT MY ARMOR BACK!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E:mad:\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERadiator spam could probably fix or at least mitigate this.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt also makes thruster melters actually viable against BDA and kinetic weapons. Adding a big cooling system in addition to your usual armor plates is probably a good idea anyways.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}